archimate:DataObject.name: PartyRevenueShare
archimate:DataObject.documentation: The amount of revenue shared among parties involved in a revenue sharing agreement. Revenue share is determined using existing artifacts such as usage; invoices; product prices; and applied billing rates. The revenue share may result in a payment to/from a party and/or an bill/invoice to/from a party. It may also be shown as a reduction of or increase to an bill/invoice sent to or received from a party; or a credit/debit to a partys account balance.
